MassFollow.net - Twitter Mass Follow 
-----------------------------------------------------------

Author: Serdar Yildirim // me[dot]serdaryildirim[dot]com
Website: http://massfollow.net
Demo Website: http://massfollow.net
Current Version: 0.2

Current Features
-----------------------------------------------------------

* Mass Manage followed people, follow/unfollow
* Search users by keywords
* Follow / Unfollow new users that found by searching

Dependencies
-----------------------------------------------------------

* ruby >= 1.9.2
* rubygems >= 1.3.7
* rails 3

Installation
-----------------------------------------------------------

* Install the dependencies
	sudo gem install bundler
	
* Download massfollow source code
	https://github.com/serdary/massfollow
	
* Change the application configs
	config/config.yml
	config/database.yml
	
* Install app dependencies
	bundle install

* Start the server
	rails s